txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Coarse fur found on beasts near Trestlebridge. Deliver the items to Guardsman Otley in the town of Trestlebridge.
'These will be put to good use. Thank you.'
'We lost much here in Trestlebridge, and we could use some assistance getting back on our feet. Furs will help us get much needed blankets made for folks in town.'
Men of Bree Task: Coarse Fur
Guardsman Otley, in Trestlebridge, is awaiting delivery of coarse fur at the war-torn town of Trestlebridge.
Deliver the coarse fur to Guardsman Otley at Trestlebridge
You have been tasked with collecting coarse fur from the beasts near Trestlebridge.\n\nYou can deliver the items to Guardsman Otley at Trestlebridge.
Wanted: Coarse fur found on beasts near Trestlebridge.
